---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
	<meta name="description" content="bae - Your music easy as streaming. Metadata-driven import from MusicBrainz and Discogs, pregap-accurate playback, encrypted storage." />
	<title>bae - Your music easy as streaming</title>
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&family=DM+Serif+Display&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
	<div class="noise"></div>

	<nav>
		<a href="/" class="logo"><img src="/sheep.png" alt="" class="logo-icon" />bae</a>
		<div class="nav-links">
			<a href="/getting-started/installation">Docs</a>
			<a href="https://github.com/bae-fm/bae" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
		</div>
	</nav>

	<main>
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="hero-content">
				<h1>Your music<br/><span class="accent">easy as streaming</span></h1>
				<p class="tagline">Scale your collection effortlessly and listen anywhere — without leaving <em>your</em> library behind.</p>
				<div class="cta-group">
					<a href="https://github.com/bae-fm/bae/releases/latest/download/bae.dmg" class="btn primary">
						<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
							<path d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.477 2 12c0 4.42 2.865 8.166 6.839 9.489.5.092.682-.217.682-.482 0-.237-.008-.866-.013-1.7-2.782.604-3.369-1.34-3.369-1.34-.454-1.156-1.11-1.463-1.11-1.463-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.03 1.531 1.03.892 1.529 2.341 1.087 2.91.831.092-.646.35-1.086.636-1.336-2.22-.253-4.555-1.11-4.555-4.943 0-1.091.39-1.984 1.029-2.683-.103-.253-.446-1.27.098-2.647 0 0 .84-.269 2.75 1.025A9.578 9.578 0 0112 6.836c.85.004 1.705.114 2.504.336 1.909-1.294 2.747-1.025 2.747-1.025.546 1.377.203 2.394.1 2.647.64.699 1.028 1.592 1.028 2.683 0 3.842-2.339 4.687-4.566 4.935.359.309.678.919.678 1.852 0 1.336-.012 2.415-.012 2.743 0 .267.18.578.688.48C19.138 20.163 22 16.418 22 12c0-5.523-4.477-10-10-10z"/>
						</svg>
						Download for macOS
					</a>
					<a href="/getting-started/installation" class="btn secondary">Read the docs</a>
				</div>
				<p class="platform-note">Windows & Linux coming soon</p>
			</div>
			<div class="hero-visual">
				<img
					src="/screenshots/library-grid.png"
					alt="bae music library showing album grid view"
					class="app-screenshot"
					onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';"
				/>
				<div class="window-frame" style="display: none;">
					<div class="window-controls">
						<span></span><span></span><span></span>
					</div>
					<div class="window-content">
						<div class="placeholder-app">
							<div class="sidebar">
								<div class="sidebar-item active"></div>
								<div class="sidebar-item"></div>
								<div class="sidebar-item"></div>
								<div class="sidebar-item"></div>
							</div>
							<div class="content-area">
								<div class="album-grid">
									<div class="album"></div>
									<div class="album"></div>
									<div class="album"></div>
									<div class="album"></div>
									<div class="album"></div>
									<div class="album"></div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="concepts">
			<div class="concept">
				<h2>Import & play</h2>
				<p>bae understands <em>releases</em>, not just files. Point it at a folder, search MusicBrainz or Discogs, and bae pulls in cover art, track listings, and release details.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="concept">
				<h2>Sync across devices</h2>
				<p>Connect a cloud provider or an S3-compatible bucket. bae creates an encrypted cloud home that holds your files, metadata, and artwork. Changes sync incrementally across devices. Keep everyday listening on fast local storage and put the rest in the cloud.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="concept">
				<h2>Share tracks</h2>
				<p>Select a track, copy a link, send it to anyone. They click and listen in their browser — no app, no account. Leave bae-desktop running locally or run bae-server headless on a VPS to keep links alive.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="concept">
				<h2>Follow libraries</h2>
				<p>Let others browse your full catalog, not just one-off links. Generate a follow code, send it to a friend, and your library appears in their bae — read-only, streaming through your server. They never touch your cloud home.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="concept">
				<h2>Curate together</h2>
				<p>Invite someone to contribute to the same library. Both of you import music, edit metadata, and curate together. bae handles access control, key distribution, and signed changesets.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="concept">
				<h2>Open source</h2>
				<p>Built with Rust and Dioxus. MIT licensed. <a href="https://github.com/bae-fm/bae" target="_blank">Contribute on GitHub</a>.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="features">
			<h2>Features</h2>
			<div class="features-grid">
				<div class="feature">
					<h3>Playback</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>CUE/FLAC albums play as individual tracks without splitting the file</li>
						<li>Gapless, pregap-accurate playback</li>
						<li>LP mode — pause at side breaks</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="feature">
					<h3>Storage</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Managed or unmanaged — bae copies files or indexes in place</li>
						<li>Google Drive, Dropbox, OneDrive, pCloud, iCloud Drive, S3-compatible</li>
						<li>End-to-end encrypted</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="feature">
					<h3>Sync</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Incremental changeset sync</li>
						<li>Automatic conflict resolution</li>
						<li>Works offline — syncs when connected</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="feature">
					<h3>Import</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>MusicBrainz and Discogs metadata lookup</li>
						<li>Cover art from Cover Art Archive and Discogs</li>
						<li>Disc ID matching for CUE sheets</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="feature">
					<h3>Sharing</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Share links — browser playback, no app needed</li>
						<li>Follow codes — read-only remote library access</li>
						<li>Shared libraries — multiple contributors, signed changesets</li>
						<li>Share grants — share individual releases across libraries</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="feature">
					<h3>Server</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Subsonic-compatible API — use any Subsonic client</li>
						<li>bae-server — headless, pulls from cloud home, streams on the fly</li>
						<li>bae-web — browser frontend for share links</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="feature">
					<h3>Identity</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Decentralized — Ed25519 keypairs, no central server</li>
						<li>Membership chain with signed entries</li>
						<li>Cryptographic attribution on every changeset</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="mission">
			<p>Music ownership shouldn't be complicated. bae exists to make owning, organizing, and playing your own music as straightforward as streaming.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="download-cta">
			<h2>Try bae</h2>
			<p>Free, open source, no account required.</p>
			<a href="https://github.com/bae-fm/bae/releases/latest/download/bae.dmg" class="btn primary large">
				Download for macOS
			</a>
		</section>
	</main>

	<footer>
		<div class="footer-content">
			<span class="footer-logo">bae</span>
			<div class="footer-links">
				<a href="/getting-started/installation">Docs</a>
				<a href="https://github.com/bae-fm/bae" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
				<a href="https://github.com/bae-fm/bae/releases" target="_blank">Releases</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</footer>
</body>
</html>

<style>
	* {
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	:root {
		--bg: #0a0a0c;
		--bg-subtle: #111114;
		--text: #e8e8ed;
		--text-muted: #8b8b96;
		--accent: #a855f7;
		--accent-dim: #7c3aed;
		--border: #1f1f24;
	}

	html {
		font-family: 'Instrument Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
		background: var(--bg);
		color: var(--text);
		scroll-behavior: smooth;
	}

	body {
		min-height: 100vh;
		position: relative;
		overflow-x: hidden;
	}

	.noise {
		position: fixed;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		pointer-events: none;
		opacity: 0.03;
		background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
		z-index: 1000;
	}

	nav {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
		max-width: 1400px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.logo {
		font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
		font-size: 1.85rem;
		color: var(--text);
		text-decoration: none;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.4rem;
	}

	.logo-icon {
		width: 120px;
		height: 120px;
		margin: -30px -20px -30px -15px;
	}

	.nav-links {
		display: flex;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.nav-links a {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}

	.nav-links a:hover {
		color: var(--text);
	}

	main {
		max-width: 1400px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 3rem;
	}

	/* Hero */

	.hero {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 4rem;
		align-items: center;
		min-height: 80vh;
		padding: 4rem 0;
	}

	h1 {
		font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
		font-size: 3.5rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		line-height: 1.15;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	h1 .accent {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent) 0%, #ec4899 100%);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
	}

	.tagline {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		max-width: 440px;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.cta-group {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.btn {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 500;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		transition: all 0.2s;
	}

	.btn.primary {
		background: var(--accent);
		color: white;
	}

	.btn.primary:hover {
		background: var(--accent-dim);
		transform: translateY(-1px);
	}

	.btn.secondary {
		background: var(--bg-subtle);
		color: var(--text);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	.btn.secondary:hover {
		background: var(--border);
	}

	.btn.large {
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.platform-note {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.hero-visual {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.app-screenshot {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 600px;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
	}

	.window-frame {
		background: var(--bg-subtle);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 12px;
		overflow: hidden;
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 500px;
		box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
	}

	.window-controls {
		display: flex;
		gap: 8px;
		padding: 12px 16px;
		background: var(--border);
	}

	.window-controls span {
		width: 12px;
		height: 12px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: #3f3f46;
	}

	.window-content {
		padding: 0;
	}

	.placeholder-app {
		display: flex;
		height: 300px;
	}

	.sidebar {
		width: 60px;
		background: #18181b;
		padding: 12px;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 8px;
	}

	.sidebar-item {
		width: 36px;
		height: 36px;
		border-radius: 8px;
		background: #27272a;
	}

	.sidebar-item.active {
		background: var(--accent-dim);
	}

	.content-area {
		flex: 1;
		padding: 16px;
		background: var(--bg);
	}

	.album-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 12px;
	}

	.album {
		aspect-ratio: 1;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #27272a 0%, #18181b 100%);
		border-radius: 6px;
	}

	.album:nth-child(1) { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #4c1d95 100%); }
	.album:nth-child(2) { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ec4899 0%, #be185d 100%); }
	.album:nth-child(3) { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #b45309 100%); }
	.album:nth-child(4) { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #047857 100%); }
	.album:nth-child(5) { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #1d4ed8 100%); }

	/* Mission */

	.mission {
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 4rem 0 6rem;
		text-align: center;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	.mission p {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-style: italic;
	}

	/* Concept sections */

	.concepts {
		padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
	}

	.concept {
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 3rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	.concept h2 {
		font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.concept p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.concept p:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.concept a {
		color: var(--accent);
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.concept a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	/* Features */

	.features {
		padding: 4rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	.features > h2 {
		font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.features-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5rem;
		max-width: 1000px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.feature {
		background: var(--bg-subtle);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 10px;
		padding: 1.5rem;
	}

	.feature h3 {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		color: var(--accent);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.feature ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.feature li {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
		padding: 0.35rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	.feature li:first-child {
		border-top: none;
		padding-top: 0;
	}

	/* Download CTA */

	.download-cta {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 6rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	.download-cta h2 {
		font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.download-cta p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	/* Footer */

	footer {
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
		padding: 2rem 3rem;
	}

	.footer-content {
		max-width: 1400px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.footer-logo {
		font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.footer-links {
		display: flex;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.footer-links a {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}

	.footer-links a:hover {
		color: var(--text);
	}

	/* Responsive */

	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.hero {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			text-align: center;
			min-height: auto;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 2.75rem;
		}

		.tagline {
			max-width: none;
		}

		.cta-group {
			justify-content: center;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.features-grid {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		nav, main, footer {
			padding-left: 1.5rem;
			padding-right: 1.5rem;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 2.25rem;
		}

		.cta-group {
			flex-direction: column;
		}

		.concept {
			padding: 2rem 0;
		}

		.features-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
